run(sql="
with cte as(
select distinct a.date, 
                a.pogId, 
                a.subOrderId, 
                a.CPT, 
                a.Channels, 
                a.NM3SO,
                case when b.availability = 'in stock' then 'IS'
                               else 'OS'
                               end as Stock, 
                case when lower(b.customLabel2) like '%cpt1%' then 'CPT1'
                               else 'No_CPT1'
                               end as CPT1,
                case when lower(b.customLabel2) like '%sale%' then 'Sale'
                               else 'No_Sale'
                               end as Sale
from(
     select distinct a.subOrderId, 
                     a.pogId, 
                     a.CPT, 
                     a.Channels, 
                     a.date, 
                     b.NM3SO 
     from(
          select distinct a.subOrderId, 
                          b.pogId, 
                          case when lower(a.utmContent) like '%cpt%' then 'CPT'
                               else 'No_CPT'
                               end as CPT,
                          case when lower(a.Channel) like 'fb%' then 'FB'
                               else 'Others'
                               end as Channels,
                          a.orderDate as date 
          from `temp.order_sd_2` a 
          left join `last3Days(agCmDump)` b 
          on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
          where DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate)>=1 
            and DATEDIFF(current_date(),a.orderDate)<=3
        ) a
     left join `temp.nmso_bau` b 
     on a.pogId=b.pogId
) a
left join `temp.FB_Live_New_Feed` b
on a.pogId=b.dmPublisherInfoId
)

select distinct date, 
                count(distinct case when Stock='IS' and NM3SO<=12 then pogId end) as LTE12_IS_Pogs, 
                count(distinct case when Stock='IS' and NM3SO<=12 and Channels='FB' then subOrderId end) as LTE12_FB_Orders_IS, 
                count(distinct case when NM3SO<=12 and Channels='FB' then subOrderId end) as LTE12_FB_Orders_OOS,
                count(distinct case when Stock='IS' and CPT1='No_CPT1' and NM3SO>12 and NM3SO<=25 then pogId end) as 12_25_IS_Pogs, 
                count(distinct case when CPT='CPT' and CPT1='CPT1' and NM3SO>12 and NM3SO<=25 and Channels='FB' then subOrderId end) as 12_25_FB_Orders_IS, 
                count(distinct case when CPT='CPT' and NM3SO>12 and NM3SO<=25 and Channels='FB' then subOrderId end) as 12_25_FB_Orders_OOS,
                count(distinct case when NM3SO>12 and NM3SO<=25 then subOrderId end) as 12_25_Orders
from cte
group by date
",1000)

from cte
